#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.0"
msgid "80. Chandaṃadatvāgamanasikkhāpada"
msgstr ""
"<hgroup><h1 id=\"Bu-Pc.80\">Monks’ Confession 80: the training rule on "
"leaving without giving consent</h1></hgroup>"

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa "
"ārāme."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"nidana\">Origin story</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.1\""
">Bu-Pc.80.1</a><a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\"BD.3.61\">BD.3.61</a><a class"
"=\"wt-pa\">1411</a>At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the "
"Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena saṃgho sannipatito hoti kenacideva karaṇīyena."
msgstr "At that time the Order had assembled on some business."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.3"
msgid "Chabbaggiyā bhikkhū cīvarakammaṃ karontā ekassa chandaṃ adaṃsu."
msgstr ""
"The monks from the group of six were busy making robes and so they gave "
"their consent to one among them.</p>"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.4"
msgid ""
"Atha kho saṃgho “yassatthāya sannipatito taṃ kammaṃ karissāmī”ti ñattiṃ "
"ṭhapesi."
msgstr ""
"<p>When the Order was ready to do the procedure for which it had assembled, "
"it set forth the motion."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.5"
msgid "Atha kho so bhikkhu—"
msgstr "That monk from the group of six thought,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.6"
msgid ""
"“evamevime ekamekassa kammaṃ karonti, kassa tumhe kammaṃ karissathā”ti "
"chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmi."
msgstr ""
"“This is just how they do procedures against us one by one, but against whom "
"will you do this one?” and without giving his consent, he got up from his "
"seat and left.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2, pts-vp-pli4.153
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.7"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1412</a>The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.8"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized him,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.9"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma bhikkhu saṃghe vinicchayakathāya vattamānāya chandaṃ adatvā "
"uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamissatī”ti … pe …"
msgstr ""
"“How can that monk <a class=\"pts-vp-pi\" id=\"Vin.4.153\">Vin.4.153</a> get "
"up from his seat and leave without giving his consent, when the Order is in "
"the process of deliberating?” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.10"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira tvaṃ, bhikkhu, saṃghe vinicchayakathāya vattamānāya chandaṃ "
"adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamasī”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monk, that you did this?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.11"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.12"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked him, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.13"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tvaṃ, moghapurisa, saṃghe vinicchayakathāya vattamānāya "
"chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamissasi."
msgstr ""
"Foolish man, how can you get up from your seat and leave without giving your "
"consent, when the Order is in the process of deliberating?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.14"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisa, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.15"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="rule">
#. REF: sc3
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:1.1.16"
msgid ""
"“Yo pana bhikkhu saṃghe vinicchayakathāya vattamānāya chandaṃ adatvā "
"uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkameyya, pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pannatti\">Final ruling</h2><p class=\"rule\"><a class=\"wt-pa\""
">1413</a>‘When the Order is in the process of deliberating, if a monk gets "
"up from his seat and leaves without first giving his consent, he commits an "
"offense entailing confession.’”</p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc4
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"pada\">Definitions</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.2\""
"></a><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.2.1\">Bu-Pc.80.2.1</a><a class=\"pts-"
"vp-en\" id=\"BD.3.62\">BD.3.62</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1414</a><term>A</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "<gloss>whoever …</gloss>"

#. HTML: </b><b class="term">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "<term>Monk</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr "<gloss>…"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr ""
"The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order through "
"a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—this sort of monk is meant in this "
"case.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </p><p><b class="term">
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.6"
msgid "Saṃghe vinicchayakathā nāma"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1415</a><term>When the Order is […] "
"deliberating</term>:"

#. HTML: </b><b class="gloss">
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.7"
msgid ""
"vatthu vā ārocitaṃ hoti avinicchitaṃ, ñatti vā ṭhapitā hoti, kammavācā vā "
"vippakatā hoti."
msgstr ""
"<gloss>when the subject-matter has been announced but the deliberation is "
"not yet concluded, or when the motion has been set forth, or when the "
"announcement is still under way.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </b></p><p><b>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.8"
msgid "Chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkameyyāti—"
msgstr ""
"<p><a class=\"wt-pa\">1416</a><term>Gets up from his seat and leaves without "
"first giving his consent</term>:"

#. HTML: </b>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.9"
msgid ""
"“kathaṃ idaṃ kammaṃ kuppaṃ assa vaggaṃ assa na kareyyā”ti gacchati, āpatti "
"dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"<gloss>if he leaves, thinking, “How may this procedure be challenged/what "
"can be done so that the assembly is incomplete/what can be done so that it "
"isn’t done,” then he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.10"
msgid "Parisāya hatthapāsaṃ vijahantassa āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he is in the process of going beyond arm’s reach of the assembly, he "
"commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.11"
msgid "Vijahite āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"When he has gone beyond arm’s reach, he commits an offense entailing "
"confession.</gloss></p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.12"
msgid ""
"Dhammakamme dhammakammasaññī chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamati, āpatti "
"pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"cakka\">Permutations</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.2\""
"></a><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.2.2\">Bu-Pc.80.2.2</a><a class=\"wt-"
"pa\">1417</a>If it is a legitimate procedure, and he perceives it as "
"legitimate, and he gets up from his seat and leaves without first giving his "
"consent, he commits an offense entailing confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.1.13"
msgid ""
"Dhammakamme vematiko chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is a legitimate procedure, but he is unsure if it is, and he gets up "
"from his seat and leaves without first giving his consent, he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.2.1"
msgid ""
"Dhammakamme adhammakammasaññī chandaṃ adatvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkamati, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"If it is a legitimate procedure, but he perceives it as illegitimate, and he "
"gets up from his seat and leaves without first giving his consent, there is "
"no offense.</p>"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.2.2"
msgid "Adhammakamme dhammakammasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"<p>If it is an illegitimate procedure, but he perceives it as legitimate, he "
"commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.2.3"
msgid "Adhammakamme vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If it is an illegitimate procedure, but he is unsure if it is, he commits an "
"offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.2.4"
msgid "Adhammakamme adhammakammasaññī, anāpatti."
msgstr ""
"If it is an illegitimate procedure, and he perceives it as illegitimate, "
"there is no offense.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
#, fuzzy
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.3.1"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr ""
"<h2 id=\"anapatti\">Non-offenses</h2><p><a class=\"pts-cs\" id=\"Bu-Pc.80.2."
"3\">Bu-Pc.80.2.3</a><a class=\"wt-pa\">1418</a>There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.3.2"
msgid ""
"“saṃghassa bhaṇḍanaṃ vā kalaho vā viggaho vā vivādo vā bhavissatī”ti "
"gacchati, “saṃghabhedo vā saṃgharāji vā bhavissatī”ti gacchati, “adhammena "
"vā vaggena vā na kammārahassa vā kammaṃ karissatī”ti gacchati, gilāno "
"gacchati, gilānassa karaṇīyena gacchati, uccārena vā passāvena vā pīḷito "
"gacchati, “na kammaṃ kopetukāmo puna paccāgamissāmī”ti gacchati, "
"ummattakassa, ādikammikassāti."
msgstr ""
"if he leaves because he thinks there will be quarreling or dispute in the "
"Order; if he leaves because he thinks there will <a class=\"pts-vp-en\" id=\""
"BD.3.63\">BD.3.63</a> be a fracture or schism in the Order; if he leaves "
"because he thinks the procedure will be illegitimate, done by an incomplete "
"assembly, or done to one who is not subject to a procedure; if he leaves "
"because he is sick; if he leaves because there is something to be done for "
"someone who is sick; if he leaves because he needs to relieve himself; if he "
"leaves with the intention to return, and not because he wants to challenge "
"the procedure; if he is insane; if he is the first offender.</p>"

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc80:2.3.3"
msgid "Chandaṃ adatvā gamanasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""
"<hr><p class=\"endsutta\"><a class=\"wt-pa\">1419</a>The tenth rule, the "
"training rule on leaving without giving consent, is finished.</p>"
